     msg‚Üê''
     msg,‚Üê‚äÇ'This function will close all Cider projects, delete everything that is not needed in order to'
     msg,‚Üê‚äÇ'run a Tatin server, re-arrange stuff, set ‚éïLX and finally save the workspace together'
     msg,‚Üê‚äÇ'with everything that is required by the server in Dist/Server.dws'
