 F‚Üê##.FilesAndDirs
 F.(APLTreeUtils2 OS)‚Üê##.(APLTreeUtils2 OS)
 :If batchFlag
 :OrIf 1 ##.Client.YesOrNo'Would you like to continue?'
     UpdateVersionNumber bumpBuild
     {}‚éïSE.Cider.CloseProject''
     #.Tatin.‚éïEX¬®'Client' 'Todo' 'TestCases' 'TestCasesServer' 'Simu' 'Tester2'
     ‚éïEX¬®'Initialize_Client' 'RunTestServer' 'CreateAllRefs_Client'
     ‚éïLX‚Üê'#.Tatin.Server.Run 1'

     F.MkDir'Dist'
